query: Can you help me organize a team meeting and share the agenda with everyone?
response: Certainly! We can use Slack for communication, Google Calendar for scheduling the meeting, and Notion for creating and sharing the agenda. First, we will create a new event in Google Calendar for the meeting, invite team members, and set the date and time. Then, we will create a new page in Notion for the agenda, outline the topics to be discussed, and share the link in Slack for everyone to access.

metadata.description: Coordinate team activities across multiple tools
